ces&gt;                 &lt;HierarchicalDataTemplate DataType="{x:Type local2:XELL_DIMENSION}" ItemsSource="{Binding DIM_ALL_NODE}"&gt;                     &lt;StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal"&gt;                         &lt;TextBlock Text="{Binding DIMEN_ID}"/&gt;                         &lt;StackPanel Orientation="Vertical"&gt;                             &lt;TextBlock Text="{Binding DIMEN_BEZ_LONG}"/&gt;                             &lt;ListBox Name="Listy" ItemsSource="{Binding XELL_ELEMS}" DisplayMemberPath="ELEM_BEZ_LONG" BorderBrush="Transparent" BorderThickness="0"/&gt;                         &lt;/StackPanel&gt;                                                 &lt;/StackPanel&gt;                 &lt;/HierarchicalDataTemplate&gt;             &lt;/TreeView.Resources&gt;                                    &lt;/TreeView&gt; </code></pre>  <p><strong>Result:</strong>  </p>  <p>hxxp://i.stack.imgur.com/Bghfs.png </p>  <p>(sorry I have no reputation points to embedd pictures and include more than two links, a rule worth consider)</p>  <p><strong>Question:</strong></p>  <p>So that's the closest I came and I used a Listbox for the Elements - but this is no Solution to me. </p>  <p><strong><em>- Any Suggestions how to solve my Problem ?</em></strong></p>  <p>I Am deeply thankful for any hint or CodeSnipped provided. </p>  <p>Excuse my non native english - Dominique</p>